# Deck Card System (Executive Summary Reference)

All list/flow cards in this deck follow the **Executive Summary visual** pattern (`ExecutiveSummaryVisual` + `VerticalFlowDiagram`).

## Card shell

- Use `gms-card rounded-2xl` for every card surface.
- Row layout: `deck-flow-step-card__row` (flex, align center, gap `1rem`).
- Title: `deck-flow-step-card__title` — **17px** default, **15px** compact (DHL-scale).

## Numbering (left)

When a step index is shown, wrap it in a **square stroke tile** — never bare text:

```tsx
<div className="deck-flow-step-card__number-col deck-flow-step-card__number-col--compact">
  <div className="deck-flow-step-card__tile deck-flow-step-card__tile--compact">
    <span className="deck-flow-step-card__number deck-flow-step-card__number--compact tabular-nums">01</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Icons (right or left)

Icons use the **same tile** as numbering. Prefer **right** via `deck-flow-step-card__icon-col`; use left only when layout requires it.

```tsx
<div className="deck-flow-step-card__icon-col deck-flow-step-card__icon-col--compact">
  <div className="deck-flow-step-card__tile deck-flow-step-card__tile--compact">
    {deckIcon(Icon, "xs")}
  </div>
</div>
```

Reuse `FlowStepTile` in `ProposalDiagrams.tsx` or `DeckIconTile` in `deck-icons.tsx` (both map to `deck-flow-step-card__tile`).

## Margins

| Element | Default | Compact |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Number column | `padding-left: 2rem` | `1.125rem` |
| Icon column | `padding-right: 2rem` | `1.125rem` |

Classes: `deck-flow-step-card__number-col`, `deck-flow-step-card__icon-col`, `--compact` variants.

## Tile sizes (CSS in `globals.css`)

- `--compact`: 2rem (panel cards: 2.125rem in dense visuals)
- `--default`: 2.5rem
- `--hero`: 5rem (appendix / large marks)

## Prefer existing components

- Vertical stacks: `VerticalFlowDiagram` with `icons` prop
- Multi-column flows: `FlowStepsVisual` / `FlowStepCard`
- Outcome lists: `DeckOutcomeCardList` (icon right, `deck-outcome-card__icon-col`)
- Feature grids: `DeckFeatureGrid` with `DeckIconTile`

Do **not** use ad-hoc `rounded-md` / `rounded-xl` icon boxes or unboxed step numbers on new deck cards.
